Hi Christian, this is Janice Patterson.

Hi Janice! How can I assist you today?

I can definitely help with that, Janice. Could I have your email address to send over some details about our inventory?

Sure, it's janice.patterson@email.com.

Thank you, Janice. And can I have your contact number in case we have any updates on the inventory?

It's four zero five five five five one two three four.

Great, thank you! I will check the stock levels for sheet music and practice keyboards and get back to you soon. Is there anything else I can help you with today?

No, that's all for now. Thank you, Christian.

You're welcome, Janice. Thank you for your time and have a wonderful day!
